until after it has been played.

1376
01:34:28,500 --> 01:34:30,000
Do you feel that to be an
especially appropriate formulation?

1377
01:34:32,000 --> 01:34:36,000
No, it certainly isn’t.

1378
01:34:38,250 --> 01:34:39,000
Because ... ?

1379
01:34:40,000 --> 01:34:42,000
Well, if you really feel compelled to play,

1380
01:34:43,000 --> 01:34:45,499
what I would consider

1381
01:34:45,500 --> 01:34:48,500
a rather superfluous tournament,

1382
01:34:50,000 --> 01:34:52,000
then surely you ought to at least

1383
01:34:53,000 --> 01:34:55,500
do it in such a way that people can
see it, if they want to.

1384
01:36:31,000 --> 01:36:35,500
No, I don’t want to speak
at length on this,

1385
01:36:36,000 --> 01:36:38,499
other than to describe
the formal situation,

1386
01:36:38,500 --> 01:36:41,000
and where we stand on principle.

1387
01:36:44,500 --> 01:36:47,000
But like I said,
they can enter the country

1388
01:36:47,500 --> 01:36:48,500
and organizations are allowed
to organize events.

1389
01:36:49,500 --> 01:36:50,999
Without the Swedish government

1390
01:36:51,000 --> 01:36:51,499
being able to stop it?

1391
01:36:51,500 --> 01:36:52,000
Yes.

1392
01:36:54,000 --> 01:36:55,000
Okay. Thank you.

1393
01:37:01,000 --> 01:37:02,499
